How is the situation?

25
00:02:10,040 --> 00:02:14,760
General, the entire Rui Royal Manor has been imprisoned together!

26
00:02:16,540 --> 00:02:18,880
Prepare a horse for me immediately! I am returning to the capital!

27
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,410
Yes!

28
00:02:57,580 --> 00:03:02,570
You brat! This is all your fault that the Rui Royal Manor is in this predicament.

29
00:03:02,570 --> 00:03:06,140
You alone deserve to die, why did you drag the entire manor into this?

30
00:03:06,140 --> 00:03:08,770
Stop making a fuss! Go back and rest!

31
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:35,110
Mother, it's all my fault. I dragged everyone into this.

32
00:03:35,110 --> 00:03:37,830
How were you wrong?

33
00:03:37,830 --> 00:03:40,640
You originally weren't willing to marry so far away.

34
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:45,390
It was they who plotted against you. What did you do wrong?

35
00:03:45,940 --> 00:03:49,720
It's just... my Jin'er has suffered.

36
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:51,880
It's fine if I suffer.

37
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:56,070
I'm afraid my child will suffer.

38
00:03:58,570 --> 00:04:04,100
Mother, don't worry. General will come and save us once he finds out.

39
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:07,720
General will certainly have a plan.

40
00:04:35,010 --> 00:04:37,760
Miss even prepared this land deed as part of my dowry!

41
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:40,110
She told me to leave, the further the better!

42
00:04:40,110 --> 00:04:43,030
I always said that I wasn't willing to die with her.

43
00:04:43,030 --> 00:04:45,510
That wasn't the truth at all.

44
00:04:45,510 --> 00:04:49,870
Now, I wish I'm the one in prison instead.

45
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:54,530
Rou Rou, don't worry. I will do whatever I can for Lord Jin.

46
00:04:54,530 --> 00:04:59,190
General will be back soon. Lord Jin will be out in a few days, too!

47
00:04:59,750 --> 00:05:02,200
You cannot lie to me.

48
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:07,210
When did I ever lie to you?

49
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:14,440
- General! <br> - General!

50
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,540
I already know the situation. I want to see my wife.

51
00:05:16,540 --> 00:05:20,600
General, His Majesty has declared that no one can see them!

52
00:05:21,350 --> 00:05:23,740
I must see my wife!

53
00:06:01,980 --> 00:06:07,190
Child... I didn't give you good food recently.

54
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:09,890
But you must hang in there!

55
00:06:10,550 --> 00:06:14,440
Once we're out, I will definitely give you delicious food!

56
00:06:36,620 --> 00:06:38,500
Jin'er.

57
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,720
You've suffered.

58
00:06:49,670 --> 00:06:52,570
Husband, why did you come so late?

59
00:06:53,350 --> 00:06:57,450
It's all my fault. I came late.

60
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:00,960
I think about you every single day.

61
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:03,800
I am eating and sleeping well here.

62
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:06,110
Don't worry, Husband!

63
00:07:06,700 --> 00:07:10,090
Don't be afraid, Jin'er. I'm here.

64
00:07:10,090 --> 00:07:12,600
I will beg His Majesty for mercy.

65
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:17,080
I'm not afraid. With you here, I am not afraid of anything!

66
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:20,180
To be able to marry you in this lifetime

67
00:07:20,180 --> 00:07:22,470
is the best thing I've ever done in my life.

68
00:07:22,470 --> 00:07:27,270
You treat me well, love me, and listen to me in everything.

69
00:07:29,250 --> 00:07:31,510
I will always remember that!

70
00:07:31,510 --> 00:07:37,200
Don't say that, Jin'er. I will definitely beg His Majesty to spare you!

71
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:39,900
Give me a few more days, all right?

72
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:42,780
No matter how long it takes, I will wait.

73
00:07:45,310 --> 00:07:47,280
Husband, you must remember.

74
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:52,210
If His Majesty won't agree, you must not offend him!

75
00:07:52,210 --> 00:07:56,840
- You must live on well and take good care of Xiuyuan! <br> - Jin'er.

76
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:59,400
I swear on the seas and mountains that I will forever love

77
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:01,820
and accompany you in this life.

78
00:08:01,820 --> 00:08:05,400
In this lifetime, I want only you.

79
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:09,280
No matter what I must do, I must save you!

80
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:13,920
Have you forgotten? We still have to go and live

81
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:16,140
on the frontier fortress with our son.

82
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:19,510
General, someone is coming.

83
00:08:19,510 --> 00:08:22,350
- Husband, hurry and go! <br> - Jin'er!

84
00:08:22,350 --> 00:08:24,920
- Hurry and go! <br> - Jin'er! <br> - Hurry and go!

85
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:27,700
Jin'er! Jin'er!

